    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/8ee6018264f31eb1fa1038b0af3beffc.poster.avif?t=1746974772\" width=800 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/8ee6018264f31eb1fa1038b0af3beffc.webm?t=1746974772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/8ee6018264f31eb1fa1038b0af3beffc.mp4?t=1746974772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意！！！本游戏需要前置摄像头方可游玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绣口吐珠》是业界首创的一款融合脸部控制技术的打砖块游戏，它革命性地以玩家的嘴巴形状作为小球挡板的即时形态。在这款游戏中，您需要在摄像头前灵活地摆动您的嘴唇以此操控挡板来反弹小球，精准地击碎砖块赢得胜利。这不仅是一场对反应速度和脸部表情动作的挑战，更是一次前所未有的趣味体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内设8章节，每章节9关，共72个精心设计的关卡，每个关卡都具有独特的砖块布局和挑战性。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/b2ab282f0fae3cea1b0a03d5aaf01e2e.avif?t=1746974772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras_big/b2ab282f0fae3cea1b0a03d5aaf01e2e.avif?t=1746974772 width=800 height=182 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种独特道具，涵盖多种增益和减益等特殊效果。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种特色砖块，种类多样，具备不同的属性和效果。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种机关设计，通过面部表情灵活操控，极具互动性和趣味性。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10种生物（含Boss战），或可爱或危险，提供多样化战斗体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/47592df089df46bf6bc1a76031e4c6be.avif?t=1746974772\" width=80 height=80 /></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/1296f040785dfc22c48f508746a55664.avif?t=1746974772\" width=80 height=80 /></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/936d74d9a748182080076fae898cb51f.avif?t=1746974772\" width=80 height=80 /></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/8a296d185f89efd25cca3891d1521539.avif?t=1746974772\" width=80 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦独特的脸部控制玩法✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脸部控制玩法新颖，直播效果极佳。还可通过解放双手，活动面部肌肉来放松身心，</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦精细的操控体验✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嘴巴的实时形状作为挡板可精细操控小球反弹，考验玩家的反应速度和操作技巧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦丰富的游戏内容和系统✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除精彩的关卡外，还提供紧张刺激的摇奖机、详尽图鉴和多彩的皮肤系统。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦关卡编辑器与创意工坊✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以自由发挥自己的创意去设计关卡，并分享到创意工坊中与其他玩家交流互动。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦全球排行榜✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过挑战最速通关时间记录来提升排名，与来自世界各地的玩家同台竞技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一场充满乐趣和挑战的打砖块游戏体验。无论你是打砖块游戏的忠实粉丝，还是想要尝试新鲜玩法的游戏爱好者或直播达人，都能在这款游戏中找到属于自己的乐趣和成就感。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126660/extras/31749f9a48a5f73deffcbc8d7f129927.avif?t=1746974772\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快来加入玩家群交流和反馈吧！QQ群：296442122</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
